javax.json

Interface JsonObjectBuilder<T>


  • public interface JsonObjectBuilder<T>
    Helps in building a JSON object. This is an intermediary class and the actual build process is started from JsonBuilder
    Author:
    Jitendra Kotamraju
    See Also:
    JsonBuilder, JsonGenerator
